PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FSurvivors still living with the
OL,7,F"devastating" medical implications of
OL,8,Fthe DES drug scandal have said they
OL,9,F"won't rest" until they get a public
OL,10,Finquiry into how the cancer-linked
OL,11,Fdrug was prescribed to pregnant women
OL,12,Fon the NHS for decades.
OL,14,FDES was a synthetic hormone prescribed
OL,15,Fto an estimated 300,000 women between
OL,16,Fthe late 1930s and 1980s to treat
OL,17,Fseveral issues, including miscarriage,
OL,18,Funtil it was linked to rare cancers
OL,19,Fand infertility in the daughters of
OL,20,Fthose who took it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FThe campaign group DES Justice UK,
OL,7,Fwhich launched following our year-long
OL,8,FITV News investigation exposing the
OL,9,Fextent of the harm caused by the drug,
OL,10,Fis made up of more than 500 survivors.
OL,12,FOn Friday, around 40 mothers,
OL,13,Fdaughters, sons and granddaughters
OL,14,Ftravelled from across the country to
OL,15,Fattend the campaign group's largest in-
OL,16,Fperson event, held in Birmingham.
OL,18,FFor many, it was the first time they
OL,19,Fhad ever met others affected by the
OL,20,Fdrug.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FSusie Martin, from Manchester, was
OL,7,Ffirst told she had abnormal cells by a
OL,8,Fgynaecologist in 2001.
OL,10,FIt was then she was asked to check if
OL,11,Fher mother had been given the drug
OL,12,Fduring her pregnancy, as she was told
OL,13,Fthe abnormal cells were "consistent
OL,14,Fwith someone who had been exposed to
OL,15,FDES".
OL,17,FNow in her 50s, Ms Martin said she has
OL,18,Fhad "between 20 and 30 operations as a
OL,19,Fresult of my mum being prescribed the
OL,20,Fdrug", and will need regular cancer
OL,21,Fscreenings for the rest of her life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,F"I've always got it hanging over my
OL,7,Fhead that it could become cancer," she
OL,8,Ftold ITV News.
OL,10,F"I have two children but I have had to
OL,11,Fspend a lot of time away from them
OL,12,Fbecause of having surgery, and I've
OL,13,Fhad to have a lot of invasive
OL,14,Fprocedures as well.
OL,16,F"It has had an emotional impact as
OL,17,Fwell as a physical impact on my life
OL,18,Fand as well as my family life."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FHer mother Jennifer Bradley said she
OL,7,Fhad been prescribed DES for the first
OL,8,Fsix months of her pregnancy in 1970,
OL,9,Fafter suffering previous miscarriages,
OL,10,Fbut claims her concerns over taking
OL,11,Fthe drug were dismissed by medical
OL,12,Fprofessionals at the time.
OL,14,FShe told ITV News: "I don't really
OL,15,Flike taking anything that's not
OL,16,Fnecessary, and because of the
OL,17,Fthalidomide scandal that had happened
OL,18,Fin the 1950s I was very sceptical, I
OL,19,Freally didn't want to take anything.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,F"I questioned it very closely, and I
OL,7,Fwas assured by the doctor that it was
OL,8,Fsafe," she added.
OL,10,FMs Bradley, who is now 82, attended
OL,11,Fthe meeting in Birmingham with her
OL,12,Fdaughter and is among those calling on
OL,13,Fthe government to launch a public
OL,14,Finquiry into why this drug was given
OL,15,Fto so many pregnant women.
OL,17,FJennifer Bradley and her daughter
OL,18,FSusie Martin spoke to ITV News at the
OL,19,FDES Justice UK campaign event in
OL,20,FBirmingham
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FWes Streeting apologised to victims
OL,7,F"on behalf of the state and
OL,8,Fgovernment" in November and urged
OL,9,Fanyone affected to contact their GP.
OL,11,FBut survivors and their families say
OL,12,Fthis doesn't go far enough and are
OL,13,Fcalling for a full statutory public
OL,14,Finquiry. They also want medical
OL,15,Fresearch into the long-term,
OL,16,Fintergenerational effects of the drug
OL,17,Fand a compensation fund to be set up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FClare Fletcher, partner at Broudie
OL,7,FJackson Canter, representing the UK
OL,8,Fvictims of the DES scandal, said an
OL,9,F"apology is not enough".
OL,11,FLast month, Ms Fletcher and Ms Martin
OL,12,Fmet with health minister Zubir Ahmed
OL,13,Fto discuss what more the government
OL,14,Fcan do to support people exposed,
OL,15,Fincluding the need for further
OL,16,Fclinical guidance and boosting
OL,17,Fresearch on the long-term harms of the
OL,18,Fdrug.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FBut campaigners were disappointed that
OL,7,Fthe Health Secretary, who had been
OL,8,Fexpected to attend, was not present
OL,9,Ffor the meeting.
OL,11,FMs Fletcher told ITV News:
OL,12,F"Accountability is a huge part of what
OL,13,Fthis campaign is looking for and when
OL,14,Fwe met with the junior minister we got
OL,15,Fsome reassurances about what is
OL,16,Fhappening in terms of education in the
OL,17,Fsector.
OL,19,F"There's been some small steps with
OL,20,Fthat, but it is nowhere near enough.
OL,21,FThe information void is still huge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,F"We intend to meet further with Wes
OL,7,FStreeting and make sure that that he
OL,8,Fand the rest of the government know
OL,9,Fthat we won't rest until we get
OL,10,Faccountability and that needs to be
OL,11,Fvia a public inquiry."
OL,13,FClare Fletcher, partner at Broudie
OL,14,FJackson Canter, representing the UK
OL,15,Fvictims of the DES scandal, said
OL,16,Fcampaigners 'won't rest' until they
OL,17,Fget a public inquiry
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
