OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FDES, originally called
OL,7,FDiethylstilboestrol, is a synthetic
OL,8,Foestrogen invented in Britain in 1939.
OL,9,FResearch suggests pregnant women who
OL,10,Ftook DES may have a 30% higher risk of
OL,11,Fbreast cancer.
OL,13,FTheir daughters, known as DES
OL,14,Fdaughters, exposed in the womb, are at
OL,15,Fan increased risk of clear cell cancer
OL,16,Fof the cervix and vagina, which is not
OL,17,Fpicked up by routine screening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FIn September, the medicines regulator
OL,7,F(MHRA) admitted it had misled the
OL,8,Fpublic for up to 25 years about when
OL,9,Fthe drug was withdrawn and issued an
OL,10,Fapology last month.
OL,12,FThe MHRA had falsely claimed that
OL,13,Fdoctors were advised to stop using the
OL,14,Fdrug for use in pre-menopausal women
OL,15,Fin 1973, a statement that our
OL,16,Freporting has exposed as inaccurate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FThe regulator then admitted that
OL,7,Finformation was incorrect, and the
OL,8,Fdrug was not stopped for use in
OL,9,Fpregnancy until the 1980s, more than a
OL,10,Fdecade after cancer risks were known.
OL,12,FFor almost three decades Suzanne
OL,13,FMassey suffered in silence, believing
OL,14,Fshe was one of the only women affected
OL,15,Fby the drug.
OL,17,FWe first met her in Liverpool when she
OL,18,Fcontacted ITV News over a year ago
OL,19,Fafter seeing one of our reports on DES.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FMs Massey believes the drug was given
OL,7,Fto her mother while she was pregnant
OL,8,Fand it is to blame for a lifetime of
OL,9,F"destructive" health problems that
OL,10,Fhave left her unable to walk at times
OL,11,Fdue to severe pain.
OL,13,FAfter years of invasive procedures,
OL,14,Fdoctors discovered anatomical
OL,15,Fabnormalities within her reproductive
OL,16,Fsystem, which was covered in rare,
OL,17,Fabnormal cells and later resulted in a
OL,18,Fhysterectomy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FSuzanne was among the those who
OL,7,Ftravelled from all over the UK to
OL,8,Fattend the event in Birmingham.
OL,10,FFor 27 years Suzanne Massey from
OL,11,FLiverpool suffered in silence,
OL,12,Fbelieving she was one of the only
OL,13,Fwomen affected by the DES drug scandal
OL,15,F"My heart is full today," she told ITV
OL,16,FNews. "Because I can't believe after
OL,17,F27 years I'm in a room with people who
OL,18,Fare going on the same journey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,F"I wanted to create a community of
OL,7,Fpeople who were affected by DES, and
OL,8,Fthis what we have done and this is why
OL,9,Fwe are here today. I could not be more
OL,10,Fproud, it's just what I wanted to
OL,11,Fachieve and we are going to take it
OL,12,Feven further."
OL,14,F"I would like the government to sit up
OL,15,Fand take notice of us, because I do
OL,16,Fbelieve it is a silent scandal," Ms
OL,17,FMassey added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773007876
OL,3,CDES drug scandal: Survivors 'won't
OL,4,Crest' until they get a public inquiry
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,FSpokesperson said: "For too long, GPs
OL,8,Fand other health professionals have
OL,9,Fbeen unaware of the impacts of DES and
OL,10,Fsupport that should be offered to
OL,11,Fthose exposed, despite so many women
OL,12,Fcontinuing to endure its devastating
OL,13,Fimpacts a generation on.
OL,15,F"This government has gripped this
OL,16,Fissue by alerting cancer alliances to
OL,17,Fensure NHS clinicians are aware of the
OL,18,Fimpacts of DES and NHS screening
OL,19,Fguidance."
OL,26,@oD@TOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
